Print a summary of a sfNetwork

Source: R/SpatialLinesNetwork.R
summary-sfNetwork-method.Rd

Print a summary of a sfNetwork

# S4 method for sfNetwork
summary(object, ...)

Arguments

object

The sfNetwork
...

Arguments to pass to relevant summary function.

Examples

data(routes_fast)
rnet <- overline(routes_fast, attrib = "length")
sln <- SpatialLinesNetwork(rnet)
summary(sln)
#> Weight attribute field: lengthIGRAPH 7705bb1 U-W- 52 80 -- 
#> + attr: x (g/n), y (g/n), n (g/n), weight (e/n)
#>                Length                 Class                  Mode 
#>                    80 SpatialLinesDataFrame                    S4
